title: Abel Court offers 1 and 2 bedroom apartments in an urban/residential!!
posting_body: Abel Court offers 1 and 2 bedroom apartments in an urban/residential setting, in Seattle's Greenwood neighborhood.
Amenities include W/D in the building, secured off-street parking.
Green Lake, Carkeek, and Golden Gardens parks are all minutes away by car.
The commercial district centered around85th and Greenwood offers a wide variety of shops and services.
Highway 99 (Aurora Ave N) is easily accessible.
PhinneyRidge, Fremont, Ballard, and Broadview neighborhoods are adjacent, with all they have to offer!
